<A>__{close on nick looking out the window as the countryside shoots past at 140 mph. from o.s. several children chanting: "harrow, harrow." nick looks over to see three uniformed school children thrusting their notebooks and pens at him.}
<B>__{joyce}
<A>__{is sitting across from nick.}
<C>__{joyce}
<D>__{they want your autograph.}
