<D>__{tell them i'm not.}
<A>__{she does, but the kids insist.}
<C>__{joyce}
<D>__{they'll never go away.}
<A>__{nick, reluctantly signs. joyce takes one of the kid's notebooks before passing it back.}
<C>__{joyce}
<D>__{mick jagger?}
<A>__{joyce smiles, surprised at his choice. then, she looks up shocked to see }
<B>__{ich}
<A>__{carrying a gift wrapped package under his arm. he's wearing his hat, blue suit and tie. ich sits across the aisle from nick and joyce. he doesn't say a word. faces straight ahead. nick looks at joyce, then back at ich.}
<C>__{nick}
<D>__{i'm sorry, ichiro. i lost it last night. i shouldn't have hit you.}
<A>__{still nothing from ich.}
<C>__{nick}
<D>__{what's in the box?}
